Combine first 4 ingredients in large self-closing plastic bag or glass dish. Add chicken; toss to coat. Refrigerate 30 minutes or longer for added flavor. Remove meat from marinade; discard marinade Preheat grill. Lightly grease grill rack. Grill chicken 5-6 minutes per side or until thoroughly cooked. Serve warm or cover and chill Thinly slice meat and layer in pita pockets or on rolls. Top with cheese, lettuce, tomato and carrots, if desired.